I"i<p>Defines a template to get the <code>available</code> state of the component. If the template returns <code>true</code>, the device is <code>available</code>. If the template returns any other value, the device will be <code>unavailable</code>. If <code>availability_template</code> is not configured, the component will always be <code>available</code>.</p>
